{"title":"Bluegrass Jetro 3/4 Shell Enduro MTB Helmet Offers More Like 4/5-Face Protection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-jetro-mips-3-4-shell-plus-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet/","date":1712319423000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_riding-with-goggles-1536x1024.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, riding with goggles\" /></p>\n<p>This new 3/4-shell Bluegrass Jetro MIPS enduro mountain bike helmet actually extends even further around your cheeks for extra face protection. Answering the call for added safety, Jetro delivers extra protection without compromising comfort and that open-face feel. And it did that by simply keeping the core of their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-vanguard-full-face-enduro-helmet/\" target=\"_blank\">Vanguard</a> full-face, and closing the loop without a chinbar. The result… 5-stars from the Virginia Tech Lab and a claim to the “best MTB helmet in test” safety title!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, extended side profile\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_side-view-768x576.jpg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Bluegrass)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve seen a boom in lightweight, well-vented <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=full+face\" target=\"_blank\">full-face helmets</a> in recent years for extra protection to match the ever-more-technical way we ride enduro and all-mountain bikes. But sometimes you just don’t want a bulky chinbar in front of your face. You want the feel of wind slapping you in the face while you ride. So more companies are making lightweight <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=3%2F4\" target=\"_blank\">3/4-shell helmets</a> too, at least offering greater coverage over your ears and the back of the head. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>But now, Bluegrass’s new Jetro 3/4-shell takes that extra protection a bit further, with moto-inspired stubs that extend cheek and side-of-the-face protection without further impacting open-face airflow.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How does it work?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, open face detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_up-close-768x576.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Effectively, it looks like the new Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4 shares the same main body as Bluegrass’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-vanguard-full-face-enduro-helmet/\" target=\"_blank\">Vanguard</a> full-face. But instead of the chinbar that is in-mold pinned to that helmet, Jetro replaces that with a tiny stubby on either side. So instead of the sides just covering your ears, this 3/4-shell extends a few centimeters further forward to protect your cheeks and probably even most of your face in a sliding of sideways crash.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, jumping\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_throwing-down-tricks-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>“With its sleek design and cutting-edge technology, this helmet offers the perfect blend of form and function, providing you with the ultimate riding experience, no matter if you wear it with goggles or without, if you use it in Dirt, Slopestyle, Enduro, or E-Bike; if you know you know!”</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details </h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, black back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_black-back-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, smoky coral side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_smoky-coral-black-side-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, moss gray angled\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_moss-gray-angled-768x768.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>In-mold polycarbonate shell with EPS liner</li>\n\n\n\n<li>MIPS C2 rotational management system</li>\n\n\n\n<li>5-star rating from the Virginia Tech Helmet Lab</li>\n\n\n\n<li>NTA 8776 certified for ebike use</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extended back head and jaw coverage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fidlock magnetic buckle makes it easier to secure the helmet</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Safety release (<em>breakaway</em>) and flexible injected visor</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Safe-T Heta fit system</li>\n\n\n\n<li>360° head belt and 3 vertical adjustments</li>\n\n\n\n<li>21 vents work in concert with internal, engineered air channeling system</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wide field of view makes it compatible with all goggles and sunglasses</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Claimed weight: 595g, in size M</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bluegrass Jetro MIPS – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding.jpg\" alt=\"Bluegrass Jetro MIPS 3/4-shell+ enduro mountain bike helmet, riding in the mud front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bluegrass-Jetro-MIPS-3-4-three-quarter-shell-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet_mudfest-riding-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Bluegrass Jetro 3/4-shell enduro mountain bike helmet is available in just one MIPS-equipped model for $270 / 250€, including a soft helmet bag. It comes in 3 sizes (S 52-56cm, M 56-58cm &amp; L 58-61cm) and is EU, US &amp; NTA 8776  ebike-certified. Jetro is available now in 3 matte color options: all-black, Smoky Coral black with red graphics, and that Moss Gray off-white with a hint of green in it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.met-helmets.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MET-helmets.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bluegrass-jetro-mips-3-4-shell-plus-enduro-mountain-bike-helmet/\">Bluegrass Jetro 3/4 Shell Enduro MTB Helmet Offers More Like 4/5-Face Protection</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"48e90ca1622b4011bfe67a50ee331c3086eaf35786fd5bdc526fff2458a288e4","category":"Cycling"}